{"tid":2111584,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"中國版 Brian Cha","createTime":"2020-07-16T15:32:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-17T04:42:44.000Z","uid":189695,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d16447840282f5a43d9c2b8f0123b9c08c88f675","tid":2111584,"uid":189695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T15:32:24.000Z","msg":"【16歲浙江少女】 【稱日作二千首詩 兼「香港注冊」媒體記者】 【被質疑多次推銷高價演講課程】<br />\n內地網絡近日熱烈討論一個「神奇小女孩」的傳說：「有這樣一個小女孩，曾經的她不會寫詩、沒有任何的基礎。可是她在一個神奇的學校，學習了三個月，她竟只花了一天時間，就寫出了兩千首詩。」<br />\n岑怡諾自稱日產二千首詩，24小時不眠不休計，要84秒內完成一首。連才高八斗、七步成詩的曹植都遇上對手，要走14000步，才可跟她打個平手。「斗酒詩百篇」的詩仙李白，相信要喝到吐完再吐，才可以和她匹敵。<br />\n在前年7月16號的時候，她還出了第三本書《岑怡諾666首詩集》。不少人想拜讀她的大作，很可惜網上遍尋不獲，岑爸爸說作品都是自資出版，只送贈朋友交流學習，出版社亦都名不經傳。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/207408373941970/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2Fvideos%2F207408373941970%2F&d=q%2BUwj3SihaKoadPXZHTFaSWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=7396a1a4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/207408373941970/</a>"},{"pid":"f6e8b2ddcbb3b2178f10681d2698908d59c835a1","tid":2111584,"uid":25169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T15:37:26.000Z","msg":"你如果唔識寫詩，就一定要睇完呢條片<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0288132c9d7ddb259479630e9d0bbe112514d08","tid":2111584,"uid":256542,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T15:38:44.000Z","msg":"未來3個月<br />\n詩界將會大洗牌"},{"pid":"70ceaf8f41981ca277c7c9b888479b02017e68b0","tid":2111584,"uid":53368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T15:48:34.000Z","msg":"都係有一部手機"},{"pid":"3cc552401d7427c5a583f1c5248984f992ed5ef5